item.title: Long cannot be dereferenced
item.dc:creator: @Scape-JAVA Scape-JAVA
item.description:
@Scape-JAVA wrote:

Post your code on www.pastebin.com, and I’ll have a look at it.

But by the looks of it, it seems as if you’re trying to treat a primitive data type (long) as an object, and you’re trying to dereference it with the period notation.
